text: John Harty (born 9 March 1941) is an Irish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
